headline: New Paychex Solution Gives Small Businesses Access to Capital
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., November 12, 2024--Paychex, Inc., a leading provider of integrated human capital management software solutions for human resources, employee benefits, insurance services, and payroll, has introduced Paychex Funding Solutions to give small- and mid-sized businesses quick access to capital as business needs arise.
